
IMAPAccount gmail
    Host    imap.gmail.com
    User    janssen.dhj@@gmail.com
    PassCmd "pass web/gmail"
    SSLType IMAPS
    CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
    Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
    Subfolders   Verbatim
    Path         ~/docs/mail
    Inbox        ~/docs/mail/INBOX
    Trash        ~/docs/mail/[Gmail]/Trash


Channel gmail
    Master :gmail-remote:
    Slave :gmail-local:
    Patterns * "![Gmail]/Spam" "![Gmail]/Trash" 
    Create Slave
    Sync All
    Expunge Both
    SyncState *
